First Department,

February, 2014

(February 4, 2014) The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v Alejendrina Simo, Appellant. [979 NYS2d 798]

An appeal having been taken to this Court by the above-named appellant from an order of the Supreme Court, Bronx County (Seth L. Marvin, J.), entered on or about April 26, 2012, and said appeal having been argued by counsel for the respective parties; and due deliberation having been had thereon, and upon the stipulation of the parties hereto dated December 30, 2013, it is unanimously ordered that said appeal be and the same is hereby withdrawn in accordance with the terms of the aforesaid stipulation.

Concur — Gonzalez, EJ., Tom, Manzanet-Daniels and Feinman, JJ.
